Solution in Solution.js is for following question :

Requirement :
Write some code, that will flatten an array of arbitrarily nested arrays of integers into a flat array of integers. e.g. [[1,2,[3]],4] -> [1,2,3,4]. 

About the solution : 
    It is written in javascript 
    To run need to install node and 
    In the directory open the terminal and run "node solution.js"

